content:
Run quick tests to see whether your workspace is set up and ready for Service Cloud Voice.

REQUIRED USER PERMISSIONS
To run the Voice Status utility: Contact Center Agent permission set

This feature is available with these telephony models:

SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH AMAZON CONNECT SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY FROM AMAZON CONNECT SERVICE CLOUD VOICE WITH PARTNER TELEPHONY

Click Check Connection to verify your Amazon Connect Endpoint. Click Run Test to verify your web browser, microphone, presence statuses, VDI, or third-party IdP.

Voice is supported only on the latest stable browser version of Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, and Microsoft Edge (Chromium). Cookies must be enabled to allow SSO.

If verification fails, messages instruct you how to debug your Voice setup.
title: Service Cloud Voice Setup and Verification
